data.description: This rare 10 acre (horse) property on a paved road will be on the market soon. This home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths in the main house while it has an attached studio with it's own entrance. Inside this home you will find a large master suite with a wood burning fireplace, 2 closets, dressing area and separate tub and shower. It also has French doors leading to the covered patio. There is a dining room which could also be used for a 4th bedroom / office in this home. This room also has French doors leading out to the covered patio. The kitchen comes with the refrigerator, oven, microwave, dishwasher and a wine refrigerator. (appliances approx. 2 years old). All you need are your pots, pans and a bottle of wine to start enjoying your kitchen. Inside the studio you will find a Murphy bed, small kitchen area and a bathroom with shower. Outside you will find a fenced yard for your privacy along with a detached 988 sq ft 3 car garage. This home has central heat and air, an evaporative cooler and a whole house water filtration system. Like to work in the garage? The garage is also cooled by an evaporative cooler. This home has a fully paid for solar system WITH battery backup ( $66,000 system). Come enjoy the desert views while still being fairly close to shopping. If you would like to enjoy Joshua Tree National Park, it is not far from this wonderful property. Don't wait as properties that offer this much for so little are a rarity.
